    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1918-11-29T08:29:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1918-11-29T08:29:00-05:00" n="688"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d688">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 861.00/3307</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Russia</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_PMGFC1"
                        type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Poole</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Archangel</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1918-11-29T17:00:00+03:31">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 29, 1918, 5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/> [<hi rend="italic">Received November 30, 7.50 a.m.</hi>]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>610. I am telegraphing <hi rend="italic">en clair</hi> No. 611 for the
                    Department’s possible criticism Thanksgiving address which I delivered before
                    soldiers at Y.M.C.A. after reading to them the most significant portions of the
                    President’s address to Congress communicating terms of armistice. Reference is
                    made to my 572, dated November 13, 3 p.m.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_PMGFC1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Poole</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
